data.name: AirOpsManager-AirlinesManagementSystem
data.description: Flight Management System using MERN Stack. It consists of an Admin Panel having specified permissions to access the database along with a Customer Panel having specified CRUD operations control and book as many tickets as they want. This was a fifth semester project for Database Systems course of FAST NUCES.

data.name: Budget-Tracker-App
data.description: Budget Tracker is a web app made with the PERN stack. It helps you manage expenses, track income, and plan savings securely. With features like Google login and clear permissions, you can trust your data's privacy. Whether it's for personal use or small-scale finance tracking, our app keeps things easy and reliable.

data.name: LeetHub
data.description: A chrome extension which automatically commits your leetcode solution to a predefined repository you connected earlier.

data.name: Urdu-News-Clustering
data.description: A web app for clustering Urdu news articles by utilizing a provided research paper. This platform efficiently organizes and categorizes similar news based on provided queries.

data.name: FacialRecognition-FlaskAPI
data.description: A Web API for adding and getting facial data written in flask which uses a face recognition system written on Python using openCV. Database could be added extensively and could be used in various authentication systems.

data.name: InformationRetrieval
data.description: This repo consists of all the assignments, projects, tasks of Information Retrieval course of FAST NUCES Spring 2023.
